{
    "componentChunkName": "component---src-templates-blog-template-js",
    "path": "/Redux/0105/",
    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"487f3b6c-6a09-5c03-befa-07b70292a705","html":"<h1 id=\"redux\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#redux\" aria-label=\"redux permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Redux</h1>\n<p>여러 컴포넌트 간의 state 문제를 해결하기 위해 등장한 상태관리 라이브러리</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.44444444444444%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"redux0.png\"\n        title=\"redux0.png\"\n        src=\"/static/909c147704599650922fe6b40c440a71/37523/redux0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/909c147704599650922fe6b40c440a71/e9ff0/redux0.png 180w,\n/static/909c147704599650922fe6b40c440a71/f21e7/redux0.png 360w,\n/static/909c147704599650922fe6b40c440a71/37523/redux0.png 720w,\n/static/909c147704599650922fe6b40c440a71/302a4/redux0.png 1080w,\n/static/909c147704599650922fe6b40c440a71/ae77d/redux0.png 1111w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"state\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#state\" aria-label=\"state permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>state</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>기본값</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"action\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#action\" aria-label=\"action permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>action</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>기본값인 state를 바꾸는것</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"dispatch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#dispatch\" aria-label=\"dispatch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>dispatch</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>이전 action으로 돌아갈 수 있는 타임머신 기능과 어떤 동작이 취해졌는지에 대한 history가 제공되기 때문에 에러 핸들링이 쉬워진다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"reducer\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reducer\" aria-label=\"reducer permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reducer</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>action이 실행되면 Reducer에서 새로운 객체가 생성되고, 기존 store의 state 객체가 새로운 객체로 <code class=\"language-text\">대체</code>된다.\naction을 받아서 새로운 state를 만들어주는 역할\ndispatch된 액션이 reducer에 걸리고, 다음 state를 만들어낸다.</p>\n</blockquote>","excerpt":"Redux 여러 컴포넌트 간의 state 문제를 해결하기 위해 등장한 상태관리 라이브러리  state 기본값 action 기본값인 state를 바꾸는것 dispatch 이전 action으로 돌아갈 수 있는 타임머신 기능과 어떤 동작이 취해졌는지에 대한 history가 제공되기 때문에 에러 핸들링이 쉬워진다. Reducer action이 실행되면 Reducer에서 새로운 객체가 생성되고, 기존 store의 state 객체가 새로운 객체로 된다.\naction을 받아서 새로운 state를 만들어주는 역할\ndispatch된 액션이 reducer에 걸리고, 다음 state를 만들어낸다.","frontmatter":{"date":"January 05, 2023","title":"Redux","categories":"Redux","author":"권형석","emoji":"😃"},"fields":{"slug":"/Redux/0105/"}},"next":{"id":"922fac00-2a47-5d4f-8856-6a45fa9847b0","html":"<blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"-에러상황\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC%EC%83%81%ED%99%A9\" aria-label=\" 에러상황 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>👨‍💻 에러상황</h1>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 719px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 40%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"blog01.png\"\n        title=\"blog01.png\"\n        src=\"/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/073e9/blog01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/e9ff0/blog01.png 180w,\n/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/f21e7/blog01.png 360w,\n/static/fa0b82c80843bab4177a00e783f0d002/073e9/blog01.png 719w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 719px) 100vw, 719px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"-어떤-에러인가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4-%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\" 어떤 에러인가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📚 어떤 에러인가?</h1>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">리액트 무한루프 렌더링</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>저장할 값을 setState에 넣을때 무한루프가 걸렸다.<br/>\n에러가 발생하는 원인은 렌더 과정에서 state를 변화하는 함수가 있다면 리랜더링이 계속 일어나면서 발생하는 에러임을 확인했다.<br/>\n(setState는 콜백으로 다시 렌더링을 트리거한다.)<br/>\nsetState는 비동기 방식으로 콜백큐가 모두 비워진 이후에 최종적으로 실행된다.<br/>\n아마 state의 계속된 변경으로 이러한 에러가 발생된듯하다.</p>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"에러-핸들링-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%90%EB%9F%AC-%ED%95%B8%EB%93%A4%EB%A7%81-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"에러 핸들링 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>에러 핸들링 방법</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">useEffect를 이용</code>하고 sideEffect로부터 보호하기.<br/>\nuseEffect <code class=\"language-text\">내부</code>에서 setState 로직을 넣어줬더니 문제 해결.<br/>\n의존성 배열을 빈배열로 놓았기 때문에 컴포넌트가 처음에 마운팅되고 난 이후에 로직실행.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">useEffect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">=></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token function\">setMyData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"컴포넌트가-리렌더링-되는-조건은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EA%B0%80-%EB%A6%AC%EB%A0%8C%EB%8D%94%EB%A7%81-%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되는 조건은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💡컴포넌트가 리렌더링 되는 조건은…</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">state</code>가 변경되었을때<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">부모컴포넌트</code>가 변경되었을때<br/>\n<code class=\"language-text\">props</code>가 변경되었을때</p>\n</blockquote>\n<br/>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"-추가로-알게된점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%EB%A1%9C-%EC%95%8C%EA%B2%8C%EB%90%9C%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\" 추가로 알게된점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>💡 추가로 알게된점</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">버튼 태그</code> 부분에서</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">const Counter = () => {\n   const [value, setValue] = useState(0);\n   return(\n       &lt;div>\n           &lt;div>{value}&lt;/div>\n           &lt;button onClick={setValue(prev => prev+1)}>+1&lt;/button>\n           &lt;button onClick={setValue(prev => prev-1)}>-1&lt;/button>\n       &lt;/div>\n   )\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">Arrow function 방식</code>으로 state를 변경해야 에러가 발생하지 않는다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;button onClick={()=>setValue(prev=>prev+1)}>+1&lt;/button></code></pre></div>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"date":"January 04, 2023","title":"Too many re-renders (SetState 관련 에러)","categories":"Error","author":"권형석","emoji":"😃"},"fields":{"slug":"/TIL/0104/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://hskwon5170.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Redux/0105/","nextSlug":"/TIL/0104/","prevSlug":""}},
    "staticQueryHashes": ["1073350324","1956554647","2938748437"]}